  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a stem of Salvia, featuring vibrant green leaves and a developing flower spike. The flower spike is in the early stages of blooming, with tightly packed, lavender-purple buds forming a slender, vertical structure. The leaves are ovate with slightly textured surfaces and a soft, velvety appearance. A delicate, lighter green stem connects the leaves and flower spike, subtly branching out. The background is a blurred, soft green, creating a sense of depth and drawing attention to the plant. The lighting is natural and diffused, illuminating the details of the plant's textures and colors.",
